title: Application of part
context: PART VIII. CORPORATE CREDIT UNION ยง412:10-800 Application of part. Provisions of this part shall govern the formation and operations of a corporate credit union. Only one corporate credit union may be chartered under this article and as such shall have the exclusive right to use the term &ldquo;corporate credit union&rdquo; as part of its name. All parts of this chapter not inconsistent with this part shall apply. [L 1993, c 350, pt of ยง1]
